summary: As Technology Architect I am the linking pin between innovation and operations for the technology domain with a holistic view, not bound by domains or projects. Understanding intrinsic characteristics and system implications of applications. Translating the business requirements to infrastructure solutions (storage, compute, virtualization, operating systems, databases, middleware, application integration).
